# Built-In Functions

| Function Header                          | Description                                       |
|------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| print(str text)                          | Prints text.                                      |
| printLine(str text )                     | Prints text and a new line.                       |
|                                          |                                                   |
| boolToStr(bool boolean) -> str           | Converts a boolean to a string.                   |
| intToStr(int integer) -> str             | Converts an integer to a string.                  |
| fltToStr(flt float) -> str               | Converts a float to a string.                     |
|                                          |                                                   |
| boolToInt(bool boolean) -> int           | Converts a boolean to an integer.                 |
| intToFlt(int integer) -> flt             | Converts an integer to a float.                   |
|                                          |                                                   |
| floor(flt float) -> flt                  | Floors a float.                                   |
| floorToInt(flt float) -> int             | Floors a float and converts it to an integer.     |
| ceil(flt float) -> flt                   | Ceils a float.                                    |
| ceilToInt(flt float) -> int              | Ceils a float and converts it to an integer.      |
| round(flt float) -> flt                  | Rounds a float.                                   |
| roundToInt(flt float) -> int             | Rounds a float and converts it to an integer.     |
| absInt(int integer) -> int               | Returns the absolute value of an integer.         |
| absFlt(flt float) -> flt                 | Returns the absolute value of a float.            |
|                                          |                                                   |
| readLine() -> str                        | Reads a line from terminal.                       |
| readChar() -> str                        | Reads a character from terminal.                  |
|                                          |                                                   |
| length(str string) -> int                | Returns the length of a string.                   |
| toLower(str string) -> str               | Converts characters of a string to lower case.    |
| toUpper(str string) -> str               | Converts characters of a string to upper case.    |
|                                          |                                                   |
| randomInt() -> int                       | Returns a random integer.                         |
| randomFlt() -> flt                       | Returns a random float from range <0,1).          |
| randomRangeInt(int min, max) -> int      | Returns a random integer from range <min, max>.   |
|                                          | Absolute value of range has to be lower or equal  |
|                                          | to the maximal value of int64.                    |
